#: addons/formerly_official_maps.wad/Formerly_Official_Maps/Elven_Forests.wmf/elemental:8
#: input:9 standard
msgid "Elven Forests"
msgstr "Elven Forests"

#: addons/formerly_official_maps.wad/Formerly_Official_Maps/Elven_Forests.wmf/elemental:10
#: input:5 standard
msgid ""
"The breath-taking beauty of these emerald lands has lured many tribes into "
"an attempt to take them for themselves."
msgstr ""
"The breath-taking beauty of these emerald lands has lured many tribes into "
"an attempt to take them for themselves."

#: addons/formerly_official_maps.wad/Formerly_Official_Maps/Europa.wmf/elemental:8
#: input:9 standard
msgid "Europa 1.2"
msgstr "Europa 1.2"

#: addons/formerly_official_maps.wad/Formerly_Official_Maps/Europa.wmf/elemental:10
msgid ""
"A huge Europe map. Blue = Sweden, Red = Italy, Yellow = Spain, Green = "
"Turkey, Black = Russia, Orange = England, Purple = France, White = Poland"
msgstr ""
"A huge Europe map. Blue = Sweden, Red = Italy, Yellow = Spain, Green = "
"Turkey, Black = Russia, Orange = England, Purple = France, White = Poland"

#: addons/formerly_official_maps.wad/Formerly_Official_Maps/Impact.wmf/elemental:9
#: input:8 standard
msgid "Impact"
msgstr "Impact"

#: addons/formerly_official_maps.wad/Formerly_Official_Maps/Impact.wmf/elemental:11
#: input:5 standard
msgid ""
"After an impact of an Asteroid and the following harsh winter, three Isles "
"are connected by Ice and stone, setting an end to the peaceful coexistence "
"of three tribes."
msgstr ""
"After an impact of an Asteroid and the following harsh winter, three isles "
"are connected by ice and stone, setting an end to the peaceful coexistence "
"of three tribes."

#: addons/formerly_official_maps.wad/Formerly_Official_Maps/Sun_of_Fire.wmf/elemental:8
#: input:9 standard
msgid "The Ancient Sun of Fire"
msgstr "The Ancient Sun of Fire"

#: addons/formerly_official_maps.wad/Formerly_Official_Maps/Sun_of_Fire.wmf/elemental:10
#: input:5 standard
msgid ""
"For hundreds of years, this island was kept as a sanctuary of the Gods. No "
"human ever ventured to set a foot on it. But now that a tribe had finally "
"been barefaced enough to settle on the coast of that island, a lot of others "
"followed in its wake."
msgstr ""
"For hundreds of years, this island was kept as a sanctuary of the Gods. No "
"human ever ventured to set a foot on it. But now that a tribe had finally "
"been barefaced enough to settle on the coast of that island, a lot of others "
"followed in its wake."

#: addons/formerly_official_maps.wad/Formerly_Official_Maps/Sun_of_Fire.wmf/elemental:11
#: input:6 standard
msgid "Start positions are clockwise"
msgstr "Start positions are clockwise"

#: addons/formerly_official_maps.wad/Formerly_Official_Maps/Twinkling_Waves.wmf/elemental:8
#: input:9 standard
msgid "Twinkling Waves"
msgstr "Twinkling Waves"

#: addons/formerly_official_maps.wad/Formerly_Official_Maps/Twinkling_Waves.wmf/elemental:10
#: input:5 standard
msgid ""
"Many beautiful, green islands await the ones brave enough to pass the "
"thousand waves, twinkling in the sun."
msgstr ""
"Many beautiful, green islands await the ones brave enough to pass the "
"thousand waves, twinkling in the sun."

#: addons/formerly_official_maps.wad/Formerly_Official_Maps/Twinkling_Waves.wmf/elemental:11
#: input:6 standard
msgid ""
"Take care not to build your ships in the lagoons. They cannot pass through "
"the reefs to the main ocean, where your ports are located."
msgstr ""
"Take care not to build your ships in the lagoons. They cannot pass through "
"the reefs to the main ocean, where your ports are located."

#: addons/formerly_official_maps.wad/Formerly_Official_Maps/Volcanic_Winter.wmf/elemental:8
#: input:9 standard
msgid "Volcanic Winter"
msgstr "Volcanic Winter"

#: addons/formerly_official_maps.wad/Formerly_Official_Maps/Volcanic_Winter.wmf/elemental:10
#: input:5 standard
msgid ""
"In the middle of summer, a series of volcanic eruptions drew the winter in. "
"Suddenly, the sun seemed to be gone and the only light and heat sources left "
"were those that enforced this dramatic change. Continents, oceans and seas "
"are frozen now, only the volcanic islands seem to be left as habitable land."
msgstr ""
"In the middle of summer, a series of volcanic eruptions drew the winter in. "
"Suddenly, the sun seemed to be gone and the only light and heat sources left "
"were those that enforced this dramatic change. Continents, oceans and seas "
"are frozen now, only the volcanic islands seem to be left as habitable land."

#: addons/formerly_official_maps.wad/addon:2
#: addons/formerly_official_maps.wad/dirnames:2 input:4 input:7 standard
msgid "Formerly Official Maps"
msgstr "Formerly Official Maps"

#: addons/formerly_official_maps.wad/addon:3 input:6 standard
msgid ""
"This map set contains all maps that were shipped with the official game at "
"some time but since removed from the map pool."
msgstr ""
"This map set contains all maps that were shipped with the official game at "
"some time but since removed from the map pool."

#: addons/formerly_official_maps.wad/addon:4 input:4 standard
msgid "The Widelands Development Team"
msgstr "The Widelands Development Team"

